'''Aman''' (H2O) d tanga yellan di wakal. Iwdan, iɣersiwen, d icakan ur zemmeren ad ddren war aman. Aman udfen deg-sen iferdisen n wuksijin (O) d uhidrujin (H). 2 i'belkimen u'hidrujin d 1 ubelkim n uksijin ttefken aneɣ aman. Aman gerrsen ɣer tfesna n 0 °C (273,15 K, 32 °F). Aman zemmren ad ilin d adfel, d agris, d amazzel (liquide), naɣ d iriggwan (water steam) (agaz).

71% n tjumma n wakal d aman. 96,5% n waman n umtiweg-nneɣ  (planet) llan deg igarawen ed yilalen, 1,7% n waman llan deg igelmamen ed yisaffen, 1,7% n waman llan deg wagris n Antarktika d Greenland, 0,001% n waman gan iriggʷan deg igenni, g usigna, g ugeffur.

